videos.headline: VT's Hooker takes it 53 yards to the house
videos.description: Hendon Hooker rushes through the middle and enjoys the open field to run it in for the Hokies' first touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VT's Hooker takes it 53 yards to the house) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hokies' Holston muscles through traffic to the end zone
videos.description: Jalen Holston does not go down easily as he forces defenders off of him to score the 8-yard rushing touchdown for Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hokies' Holston muscles through traffic to the end zone) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurricanes' King walks in for the 10-yard TD
videos.description: D' Eriq King shakes a defender and easily makes it to the end zone giving Miami their first touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurricanes' King walks in for the 10-yard TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: VT's Holston reaches out for the goal line
videos.description: Jalen Holston makes it through the defensive traffic to score the 1-yard touchdown for the Hokies.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VT's Holston reaches out for the goal line) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami's Wiggins crashes into kicker's net
videos.description: Running a route, Dee Wiggins gets forced out of bounds and crashes into the kicking net on the Hurricanes' sideline.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami's Wiggins crashes into kicker's net) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris cuts into Virginia Tech's lead with a TD
videos.description: Cam'Ron Harris rushes through the middle and scores a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris cuts into Virginia Tech's lead with a TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: King, Pope connect to put the Canes ahead
videos.description: D'Eriq King finds Mark Pope Jr. for the 36-yard touchdown, giving Miami its first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (King, Pope connect to put the Canes ahead) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: King, Miami rally to edge out Virginia Tech
videos.description: D'Eriq King connected with Mark Pope late in the game for a crucial passing touchdown in Miami's 25-24 win over Virginia Tech.
